Mollie L. G. EUBANKS, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 11576. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Oct. 30, 1946. H. M. Powell, of Birmingham, Ala., for appellant. John D. Hill, U. S. Atty., and Gorman R. Jones, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Birmingham, Ala., for appellee.

Before HOLMES, McCORD, and LEE, Circuit Judges.

For failure to comply with Rule 23 of this Court, the appeal is dismissed.
